race.comment: STATE OF FURY (8) got the job done first-up at Bunbury, scoring by 0.4L over the 1200m journey. This is tougher, but she rates highly on that effort and boasts a strong record at this track and trip. Needs come luck from the gate but carries no weight and can go back-to-back. TRUE PLAYER (5) looks primed for a bold effort on resumption on the back of a nice trial at Lark Hill recently. Pike hops in the saddle for his racing return and he looks a nice gelding on the way up. Short of his best trip here but can play a leading role. ZAC LUVS TO FLY (12) missed by 0.1L two back at Bunbury before a 5L defeat at Mt Barker last time out. Out to 1400m now and his run two back stacks right up in this field. Can play a leading role. IDYLLIC RULER (1) can sit handy and be in the finish on resumption. JUST LEROY (7) has trialled well coming into this and can make his presence felt.
